sub_title: Italian market customer service and sales, Antiquarian books acquisition and price quotation handler
summary:
Professionalism, trust, empathy, reliability and efficiency were the fundaments of my character, and fundaments for all my job experiences.
In fact, these values were important when I was managing the migrant's department of the Cooperativa Ellepikappa, when I was teaching Italian language to my students, while I was doing legal counseling, or with clients and managers when I was working at the Libraccio bookshops. 
I always learned and got the best from all the people and environments that I encountered on my path. My passions are reading, music and travel. I am interested in the web in general and its dynamics, everything internet-related, and digital communication.
